    @NextUpdate
public class DefaultMixtureRM
extends net.hudup.core.alg.ExecutableAlgAbstract
implements RM, RMRemote, net.hudup.core.alg.MemoryBasedAlg, net.hudup.core.alg.MemoryBasedAlgRemote, net.hudup.core.alg.DuplicatableAlg
    This class represents the default mixture regression model. This class needs to be improved because the algorithm (fitness function) to specify the number of sub-models (components) is not perfect.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Loc Nguyen
